title: Spawn HBO Series, Seasons 1,2,and 3
description:
This was originally three dual sided DVD&#039;s. Each side contains a little over an hour, or about half of the season.

I took these DVD&#039;s and used #1 DVD ripper with DIVX codec on "insane" quality at 3250 bitrate, and dual pass mode. The sound is 320k Mpeg layer 3 codec. Since this is a cartoon, the quality degradation is quite minimal as compared with the original.
